e-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">W</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">m</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">1</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">N</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">l</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">k</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">N</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">，</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">一</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">个</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">学</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">生</span></span><span class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\"> </span></span><span class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">&amp;</span></span><span class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\"> </span></span><span class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">一</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">瓶</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">牛</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">奶</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">。</span></span></p></div><div><p style=\"opacity:0\"><span class=\"sr-only\">平时喜欢记录一些日常，深度沉迷互联网又想在信息汪洋中有个锚点，于是便有了这个博客。</span><span class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">平</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">时</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">喜</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">欢</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">记</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">录</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">一</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">些</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">日</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">常</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">，</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">深</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">度</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">沉</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">迷</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">互</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">联</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">网</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pre\" style=\"opacity:0\">又</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"inline-block whitespace-pr